# Checking outliers
rows = 2
cols = 2
fig, axs = plt.subplots(rows,cols)
index=-1
for i in range(rows):
  for j in range(cols):
    index+=1
    axs[i,j].boxplot(df[df.columns[index]])
    axs[i,j].set_title(df.columns[index])
fig.set_size_inches(20,10)
fig.show()
